=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Singular_value_deco=
mposition#cite_note-FOOTNOTEHastieTibshiraniFriedman2009535%E2%80%93536-7">=
<span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>6<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span>=
</a></sup>
</p><p>Let <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span c=
lass=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none=
