=3D28" title=3D"Edit section: One-sided Jacobi algorithm"><span>edit</span>=
</a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>One-sided Jacobi algorithm is an iterative algorithm,<sup id=3D"cite_ref=
-26" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Singular_=
value_decomposition#cite_note-26"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>24<s=
pan class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
