</a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Two-sided Jacobi SVD algorithm=E2=80=94a generalization of the <a href=
=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacobi_eigenvalue_algorithm" title=3D"Jac=
obi eigenvalue algorithm">Jacobi eigenvalue algorithm</a>=E2=80=94is an ite=
rative algorithm where a square matrix is iteratively transformed into a di=
agonal matrix. If the matrix is not square the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipe=
dia.org/wiki/QR_decomposition" title=3D"QR decomposition">QR decomposition<=
/a> is performed first and then the algorithm is applied to the <span class=
=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathm=
l-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http=
